Depends: dialog, initrd-tools, perl, bash (>>2.05), lilo, kdm, grub-gfxboot | grub, whois, yaird, initscripts-kanotix, ifrename, kanotix-udev-config, initscripts-kanotix-live
Suggests: qtparted, xdialog, fix-cdrom, distro-defaults, 855resolution
Description: installs kanotix to hd
 kanotix-installer is an fully functional installation program
 to easily install kanotix to hd. It has support for config-files, 
 which allow more advanced usages.

